               <lb/><milestone unit="line" edRef="S-4b"/>river–and he dropped down with- <lb/>out
               obstruction, from Sudbury, where <lb/>he lived; to Fair Haven Pond, which <lb/>he
               found unexpectedly, <mod><handShift medium="pencil"/><del rend="hzag">was</del></mod>
