                     place="above">for the most part</add></mod>
               <lb/>with a firm field of ice. It was a <mod><handShift medium="pencil"/><add
                     place="inline">–</add></mod>
               <lb/><mod><handShift medium="ink2"/><del rend="vzag">very</del></mod> warm spring
               day, and he was <lb/><mod><handShift medium="ink2"/><del rend="hstrike"
                     >astonished</del><add place="above">surprised</add></mod> to see such a body of
               ice <lb/>remaining. Not seeing any ducks <lb/>he hid his boat on the <mod
                  type="insert"><handShift medium="pencil"/><metamark rend="caret" place="inline"
